         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Bank, for year 3, through Theon.;Pharmouthi:;Petermouthis, son of ditto: 28;Equal 28 drachmai;;(2nd hand) Pauni:;Horos, son of Harphaesis: 44 (drachmai) 2 chalkoi, (and) 1 (drachme) 1 obol;Nekpheros, son of Horos: 32;Apynchis, son of Apynchis: 16 (drachmai) 1/2 obol 2 chalkoi, (and) 1 (drachme) 1 obol;(1st hand) Pabones, son of Sambas: 28 (drachmai) 1/2 obol 2 chalkoi, (and) 1 (drachme) 1 obol</ab>
         </div>
